  "detailed_description": "<h1>Update Notes</h1><p>Ver 1.3<br>- Fixed an unintended action in the stage 6 coffee table position.<br>- The stage 6 clock hints after the player sees the true portrait.<br><br>Ver 1.2<br>Update<br>- Add the Options menu to adjust the volume and treasure chest rewards.<br>- Replace \"Perfect\" voice.<br>Fix<br>- Fixed the problem that the game would freeze when leaving without getting the treasure.<br>- Fixed the problem that the hiding point on the right can be moved to the boss level of the 6th stage.<br>- Fixed an issue where the shop icon was incorrect.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>This is a funny action game without language barriers.<br>Operate the phantom thief Bunny Moon to steal the treasures of each stage, <br>and watch Bunny Moon's fantasy adventure!<br><br>Time Thief is a 2D pixel action game. <br>Players operate the protagonist \"Bunny Moon\" entering the place of many guards, <br>to steal treasures from different eras. <br>But be careful, you are not the only trespasser in the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/872fe2eff8a3925321f59dab4f1d0e6c.poster.avif?t=1689409511\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/872fe2eff8a3925321f59dab4f1d0e6c.webm?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/872fe2eff8a3925321f59dab4f1d0e6c.mp4?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As a phantom thief, Bunny Moon has a variety of abilities to do her job.<br>Since the name of the game is Time Thief, <br>besides being able to travel through time, of course, <br>she can also stop time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/99c716ea1eac4a058c40055743cada07.poster.avif?t=1689409511\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/99c716ea1eac4a058c40055743cada07.webm?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/99c716ea1eac4a058c40055743cada07.mp4?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Become a Phantom Thief!<br>Use a variety of Phantom Thief abilities to steal all the treasures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/e141f9c01215d6f45234fed27c4b3f31.poster.avif?t=1689409511\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/e141f9c01215d6f45234fed27c4b3f31.webm?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/e141f9c01215d6f45234fed27c4b3f31.mp4?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "This is a funny action game without language barriers.<br>Operate the phantom thief Bunny Moon to steal the treasures of each stage, <br>and watch Bunny Moon's fantasy adventure!<br><br>Time Thief is a 2D pixel action game. <br>Players operate the protagonist \"Bunny Moon\" entering the place of many guards, <br>to steal treasures from different eras. <br>But be careful, you are not the only trespasser in the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/872fe2eff8a3925321f59dab4f1d0e6c.poster.avif?t=1689409511\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/872fe2eff8a3925321f59dab4f1d0e6c.webm?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/872fe2eff8a3925321f59dab4f1d0e6c.mp4?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As a phantom thief, Bunny Moon has a variety of abilities to do her job.<br>Since the name of the game is Time Thief, <br>besides being able to travel through time, of course, <br>she can also stop time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/99c716ea1eac4a058c40055743cada07.poster.avif?t=1689409511\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/99c716ea1eac4a058c40055743cada07.webm?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242610/extras/99c716ea1eac4a058c40055743cada07.mp4?t=1689409511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Become a Phantom Thief!<br>Use a variety of Phantom Thief abilities to steal all the treasures.<